    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 450ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[675ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[900ml]</span> <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water </strong>– this is your <strong>chicken stock</strong></p>",
