    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the carrot and potato are fork-tender, stir through your <strong>soft</strong> <strong>cheese</strong> and season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>bacon, leek & potato chowder</strong></p>",
